OL,3,CFarmers urge government to give them
OL,4,Ccontrol of Guernsey Dairy
OL,6,Ffarmers are calling on the island's
OL,7,Fgovernment to allow them to control
OL,8,Fthe island's dairy and decide its
OL,9,Ffuture.
OL,11,FThere are 11 farmers on Guernsey who
OL,12,Flook after 20% of the island's land
OL,13,Fand they want to echo in running the
OL,14,Fdairy themselves.
OL,16,FThe President of Guernsey Farmers
OL,17,FAssociation, Michael Bray, says: "Why
OL,18,Fis the States of Guernsey running a
OL,19,Fdairy when they don't know anything
OL,20,Fabout dairy farming or dairying?
