OL,3,CFarmers urge government to give them
OL,4,Ccontrol of Guernsey Dairy
OL,6,F"No one else seems to do it in any
OL,7,Fother jurisdiction, so we need to look
OL,8,Fat all the options."
OL,10,FA major issue in Guernsey Dairy's
OL,11,Ffuture is funding.
OL,13,FIt says it will need more than #6.25
OL,14,Fmillion to continue operating for the
OL,15,Fnext five years.
OL,17,FThe money would be used to fund the
OL,18,Frepairs and maintenance of the ageing
OL,19,Ffacility which was deemed "not fit for
OL,20,Fpurpose" by the States in 2020.
