OL,6,FChairman of Guernsey Dairy, Mark
OL,7,FThompson, says: "Four years ago there
OL,8,Fwas a policy letter where the building
OL,9,Fwas described as not fit for purpose,
OL,10,Fit's just past its sell-by date.
OL,12,F"In most parts of Europe, farms are
OL,13,Fsupported by the Government and that
OL,14,Fhappens in Guernsey too, but farmers
OL,15,Fget #1 million a year direct from the
OL,16,FStates.
OL,18,F"20 years ago that was #2 million so
OL,19,Fthat's a lot of money that they aren't
OL,20,Fgetting now.
