OL,4,Ccontrol of Guernsey Dairy
OL,6,F"Environment and Infrastructure are
OL,7,Fputting together a policy letter
OL,8,Flooking at the future of farming and
OL,9,Fwe are hoping that that will address
OL,10,Fthe balance of how farmers are
OL,11,Fsupported."
OL,13,FThe Policy and Resources Committee
OL,14,Fwill have to approve funding for the
OL,15,Fdairy business as part of the
OL,16,Fbudgeting process but farmers are
OL,17,Fconcerned that without it, Guernsey
OL,18,FDairy will not be viable in its
OL,19,Fcurrent form.
