OL,3,CFarmers urge government to give them
OL,4,Ccontrol of Guernsey Dairy
OL,6,F"We believe that we could knock a
OL,7,Fmillion pounds a year off the running
OL,8,Fcosts, run it with far fewer people,
OL,9,Fbut we have to accept that the States
OL,10,Fhave decided that hospitals and
OL,11,Fschools at this moment are far more
OL,12,Fimportant than funding a dairy.
OL,14,F"The new dairy has to come fairly soon
OL,15,Fbecause the current one is well past
OL,16,Fits shelf life and we're having to
OL,17,Fpump quite a lot of capital money into
OL,18,Fnew equipment inside the old dairy,
OL,19,Fnot all of which will be transferable
OL,20,Fto a new dairy, so that is incredibly
OL,21,Ffrustrating."
